  "description": "<i>clever! Das Spiel, das Wissen schafft</i> is a puzzle game based on the German TV show <i>clever! Die Show, die Wissen schafft</i>. It is played the same way as the <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?gamegroup=Incredible+Machine+series\">Incredible Machine</a> or the more recent <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/search/quick?gamegroup=Crazy+Machines\">Crazy Machines</a> series. The player faces about 100 tasks, e.g. filling an aquarium with water. To do so he has a limited amount of gizmos to his disposal which he needs to arrange correctly so they perform chain reactions. \nOverall there are about 50 of them, e.g. conveyor belts or steam engines. ",
